sp23_barcrawl.eventDetails: Join ACM and meet your fellow members as we visit Murphy's, KAMS, Joe's, and Legends on our semesterly bar crawl. Get a free t-shirt with sign-up. Alcohol will be provided by ACM to members over 21 wearing bar crawl t-shirts. However, this ticket does not pay for cover at the bars.
sp23_barcrawl.eventCost: $10 for paid ACM members,  $13 for nonmembers
